      "anatomy": "<div rdxMeterRoot [value]=\"24\">\n  <span rdxMeterLabel>Storage used</span>\n  <div rdxMeterTrack>\n    <div rdxMeterIndicator></div>\n  </div>\n  <span rdxMeterValue></span>\n</div>",
